bibliothek.gui.dock.station.toolbar.group

Class AbstractToolbarGroupActions<P,C extends AbstractToolbarGroupActions.Column>

  • java.lang.Object
    • bibliothek.gui.dock.station.toolbar.group.AbstractToolbarGroupActions<P,C>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of object that represents a Dockable
    C - the type of this subclass
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ColumnDockActionSource
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExpandToolbarGroupActions

    public abstract class AbstractToolbarGroupActions<P,C extends AbstractToolbarGroupActions.Column>
extends Object
implements ColumnDockActionSource
    A class that can create one DockActionSource for each ToolbarColumn a ToolbarGroupDockStation has. This class is built such that subclasses can easily access or modify the DockActionSources.
    Author:
    Benjamin Sigg
